text: Daniel Llambrich Gabriel (born December 8, 1978 in Inca, Balearic Islands) is a swimmer from Spain. He has a disability: he is an S9 type swimmer. He raced at the 1996 Summer Paralympics. He finished third in the 4 x 100 freestyle 34 points relay.
